verse = \lyricmode {
  God shamed his foes with words that sting:
\"At E -- dom I my san -- dal fling;
I Mo -- ab as my wash -- bowl claim
and in Phi -- lis -- tia shout my fame.\"
God, who but you can be our guide
to E -- dom, so well for -- ti -- fied?
But you have cast us off in an -- ger
and with our ar -- mies march no lon -- ger.
}
